rComments: SHE IS THE DVM GOAT. Attend her lectures, very interesting and helpful. I had to work so couldnt attend all her lectures but ended up with an A. Feedback is clear and prepares you! Tas super helpful and smart. I will be taking more of her classes.

She is sweet but low energy. I wasn't in love with her teaching or the material. There are 3 papers worth 20% each, 10% participation and the final (30%) that's a take home essay. She invited many guests towards the end of the course which sometimes got redundant. The class was never recorded and students had to ask for the notes to be published.
